## Room-by-Room

- Entry/mudroom: storage, winter gear flow, stroller/kid gear, shoe drop.
- Kitchen: layout, sightlines, pantry, appliance condition, cabinet quality.
- Bedrooms: kid-room proximity, noise, closet space, stairs, bathroom access.
- Basement: smell, moisture signs, ceiling height, sump/drain tile, finished-space quality.
- Garage/driveway: stall depth, slope, snow storage, alley/plowing, EV or tool storage.
- Yard: usable flat area, drainage, privacy, fence, mature trees, maintenance burden.

## Verify Before Offer

- Disclosures and seller property condition statements.
- Mechanical ages and permits.
- Sewer scope or sewer-line history.
- Public tax, parcel, and school boundary facts.
- Insurance claim history if available through disclosures.
